articles.author: Yaseen Rana
articles.title: Mark out of 10: England player ratings after their ODI series defeat to West Indies - Wisden
articles.description: England’s post-World Cup reconfiguration started unconvincingly with a 2-1 defeat against a West Indies side that failed to make the World Cup.
articles.content:
Englands post-World Cup reconfiguration started unconvincingly with a 2-1 defeat to an understrength West Indies side that failed to get through this years World Cup Qualifier.
